19
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:48,220
=Episode 13=

20
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,599
Zitong, you're here.

21
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,720
I'll give you 10 minutes.

22
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,940
What do you want to say? Say it now.

23
00:01:59,839 --> 00:02:00,760
Do you want any drinks?

24
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,680
Nine more minutes.

25
00:02:04,839 --> 00:02:06,000
Is this how...

26
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:09,220
we're going to talk to each other
in the future?

27
00:02:11,399 --> 00:02:12,319
Why?

28
00:02:12,399 --> 00:02:13,720
Are you upset?

29
00:02:14,279 --> 00:02:15,119
If you feel upset,

30
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:16,520
you shouldn't have done
what you did three years ago.

31
00:02:17,839 --> 00:02:20,360
To be honest,
I didn't plan to meet you today.

32
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:23,641
But I heard you've been bothering everyone
for the past few days.

33
00:02:23,721 --> 00:02:25,241
You asked my brother
and my sister-in-law out.

34
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,475
Oh, yes.

35
00:02:27,559 --> 00:02:30,240
I guess you've already found out
about my brother's marriage.

36
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,679
Yes, I have.

37
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:35,960
I asked them out...

38
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,759
for a catch-up.

39
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:39,319
A catch-up?

40
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:44,039
It seems like you disregarded what I said.

41
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,919
Fine. I'll remind you once again.

42
00:02:49,839 --> 00:02:51,679
Don't even think about plotting anything.

43
00:02:51,759 --> 00:02:54,199
If you dare break up their marriage,

44
00:02:54,279 --> 00:02:55,960
I won't show you any mercy.

45
